data.description: MUST SEE!!! Large corner lot, well cared for 4bdr 2bth home, Many upgrades, Kitchen w/large island w/kitchen sink, Walk in Pantry, 7 ceiling can lights in kitchen. Large Master Bedroom, w/Dual Sinks in M/bath, Separate Tub/shower, Heater & infrared light in shower area, Walk in closet & linen closet in. Living room, Dining room, 2nd bath w/dual sinks, Ceiling fans throughout home, tile & carpet in the right places, Front porch, Exterior Sunscreen, Covered patio in back for entertaining friends & family w/beautiful mountain views. Front and rear home landscaping, Freshly painted outside home(7/16), shopping/restaurant''s/entertainment/hospital close by. Ready to move right in!!!!
